name: Susan Bello Adeola
description: I consider myself to be a caring, loving, confident, smart, sweet, and very kind human being. I value honesty and good manners. I’m a very simple person but at the same time, I have style and presence. I respect good values and hard work. I do believe in true love, and the commitment that it takes while you are in one. I love to travel and have fun… I’m passionate and loving….I believe that trust and open communication can prevent misunderstandings in a relationship and prevent pain, which I’m sure we all have experienced one or many times in a lifetime.
